Enum Class DuelGameMode

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<DuelGameMode>
com.conquest.duelHandler.duelRequestHandler.DuelGameMode
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<DuelGameMode>, Constable
public enum DuelGameMode extends Enum<DuelGameMode>
🎮 DuelGameMode Represents all unique XvY combinations (unordered: 1v3 == 3v1). Backed by parsed team sizes for A and B.
